r ecosystem, hasn=E2=80=99t been bothered by Siri=E2=80=99s disappointing p=
erformance. And, to the extent a headset era is beginning, it=E2=80=99s rea=
sonable to expect that Apple=E2=80=99s usual advantages, particularly in te=
